cast.overview: Ray and Ken, two hit men, are in Bruges, Belgium, waiting for their next mission. While they are there they have time to think and discuss their previous assignment. When the mission is revealed to Ken, it is not what he expected.
cast.title: In Bruges

details.biography: Jordan Prentice, a Canadian actor known for his roles in various films and music videos, identifies as a "person of short stature." He gained recognition for portraying characters like Rock in "American Pie Presents: The Naked Mile" and Jimmy in "In Bruges." Notably, Prentice appeared in music videos for Vengaboys' "Shalala Lala" and The Bloodhound Gang's "The Bad Touch," showcasing his versatile performances across different media.
details.name: Jordan Prentice
